channel.title: Can a compiler do this to my laptop?
channel.description:
So i was working on a server and i had compiler errors but i still continued to use my server with the errors on, eventually my laptop starting messing up and now everytime i open up a folder i get the message 'Windows explorer has stopped working'. Does this mean my laptop has corrupt files?
can someone shine a light on this please? Thankyou.
